{"tid":249371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有片】【有圖】台妹全裸鎖鏈反鎖雙手逛大街","createTime":"2017-05-19T08:59:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-19T09:37:47.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"44cce932590415334aebed9d34be327870e58680","tid":249371,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T08:59:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170514/640_b48e4da5974935d062a02f8783279985.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170514%2F640_b48e4da5974935d062a02f8783279985.jpg&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=50970e5a\" target=\"_blank\">http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170514/640_b48e4da5974935d062a02f8783279985.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170514/640_1bfd91be2bf1b868cf845b69ad74f512.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170514%2F640_1bfd91be2bf1b868cf845b69ad74f512.jpg&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=5721e8db\" target=\"_blank\">http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170514/640_1bfd91be2bf1b868cf845b69ad74f512.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">【有片】【有圖】台妹全裸鎖鏈反鎖雙手逛大街</span></strong><br />\n2017/05/14 22:42<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://rtnvideo1.appledaily.com.tw/mcp/encode/2017/05/14/3345943/1118596_360p.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frtnvideo1.appledaily.com.tw%2Fmcp%2Fencode%2F2017%2F05%2F14%2F3345943%2F1118596_360p.mp4&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=078d2c9f\" target=\"_blank\">http://rtnvideo1.appledaily.com.tw/mcp/encode/2017/05/14/3345943/1118596_360p.mp4</a><br />\n<br />\n(新增：影片)<br />\n台北市火車站旁的忠孝西路上，今天下午有民眾拍攝一段影片。影片中只見疑似一名女性，身上盤繞著鐵鍊，雙手反綁在背，全身一絲不掛，連鞋子都沒穿在騎樓下行走，路過民眾無不側目觀看，實際詢問轄區派出所卻沒有相關人士報案。<br />\n<br />\n今天下午2時許，民眾在台北市火車站旁忠孝西路上拍攝一段影片，內容是一名疑似女性全裸，身上纏著鎖鏈、雙手反綁在背，步行在騎樓下，跟她擦身而過的民眾都狐疑地回頭觀看。實際詢問旁邊的店家，便利商店店員說並沒有看到該名裸女，也沒有聽說；而另一家咖啡店員則說，在下午2時許的時候，聽說有人看到一名女生，全身赤裸，臉上戴著面具，身上綁著類似狗鍊的東西，在騎樓下行走，但不知道她的目的是什麼。轄區派出所表示近日並沒有接獲類似妨害風化的案件，也沒有民眾打來投訴有裸女在街上遊蕩，日後將會加強轄區的安全巡邏，並呼籲民眾不要全裸在街上行走，否則將會觸犯妨害風化罪嫌。（突發中心陳以昇／台北報導）"},{"pid":"23746529f9e2bb7b9a2337ce22bdec8682b9bc29","tid":249371,"uid":39365,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T09:03:09.000Z","msg":"應係女奴俾主人TRAIN緊"},{"pid":"6d6c77b3c480db8adfffe9fee479eb88770131e0","tid":249371,"uid":3656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T09:08:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應係女奴俾主人TRAIN緊</blockquote><br />\n行為藝術嘅嘢你識條春咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：我都唔識"},{"pid":"1ca8814c43e0223fc36555a655a060cc9bcb8e62","tid":249371,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T09:36:12.000Z","msg":"我射左"},{"pid":"3cf2c8abeac31b58d2905c6441020315b2c345af","tid":249371,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T09:37:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>臉上戴著面具</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.ebayimg.com/images/g/9csAAOSwaA5WikyV/s-l300.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.ebayimg.com%2Fimages%2Fg%2F9csAAOSwaA5WikyV%2Fs-l300.jpg&h=878fe37b&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}